00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:09.373
Billions is what they're saying. So all that I was talking about and what the Lord showed me in my prayer time is legit.

00:01:09.374 --> 00:01:19.266
Obviously, when you're using software from 1995, and it's 30-year-old software, and you're using computers with floppy disks, I mean, this is a major deal.

00:01:19.267 --> 00:01:31.305
We're going into a new industrial revolution with 1995 software, with AI technology using quantum computers, and we have 1995 software with AI.

00:01:31.306 --> 00:01:42.179
So obviously, when you have other countries being able to tap into the AI and hack into our infrastructure, it's probably not going to be that hard.

00:01:42.180 --> 00:01:50.004
I wonder if they're using dial-up, you know? I mean, and it's like, no, this is not cool.

00:01:50.005 --> 00:01:57.671
And they're saying it could take up to four years, so that's all of President Trump's term, clear up past it.

00:01:57.672 --> 00:02:09.678
I mean, that's a major deal. So, that was part of it. Then, right after that, we see the airlines that the Lord spoke to me about.

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:12.923
One was on fire and had to do an emergency landing in the middle of the air.

00:02:12.924 --> 00:02:16.478
This is another sign of something that the Lord's trying to warn everybody about.

00:02:16.479 --> 00:02:28.223
Right after I give you the word, not even 24 hours later, there's a plane and it's caught fire in the middle of the air, and it has to do an emergency landing, and you can see people filming it and it's burning and doing all this stuff.

00:02:28.224 --> 00:02:36.782
And I thought, 'Lord, you're speaking so loud trying to warn your people to pray.'You know, like I said, God has not called us to fear; He has called us to pray.

00:02:36.783 --> 00:02:42.318
