00:02:48.782 --> 00:02:55.312
I was assuming cyber attacks, but how could you get to the plane and turn it off? I have no idea.

00:02:55.313 --> 00:03:03.381
All I know is I saw a plane; its dash went completely blank and it fell, and it was very dangerous.

00:03:03.382 --> 00:03:12.132
I could tell you where it was leaving from. It was leaving from the central part of America and it was going northeast.

00:03:12.133 --> 00:03:18.865
It was going northeast to like the Boston area, and this was a major flight, and it was halfway there and it went down.

00:03:18.866 --> 00:03:23.065
I can tell you that's what it looked like. Now, is that going to be every plane?

00:03:23.066 --> 00:03:30.989
And is that just something that the Lord's trying to show us, is what I'm trying to say, or is that the exact flight?

00:03:30.990 --> 00:03:42.639
